Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate everything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This sunshine, beating down \Non you from morning onward...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:47.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,These students, who don't have \Na thought in their heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:51.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And having to hike up this steep \Nslope every day from today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,just to get to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:01.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It all makes me want to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:11.50,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.73,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Joining us from today is Nishimi \NKaoru-kun, all the way from Yokosuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:15.36,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was at the top of his \Nclass at his previous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.10,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I hope all of you study just as hard as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:21.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nishimi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:22.02,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yokosuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.29,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Isn't that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to this routine. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:26.64,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He looks like a real grind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.85,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Spoiled rich kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:28.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Their unreserved stares...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Their Kyushu dialect that I can't follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most memorable \Nwelcome I've received yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.32,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun. Nishimi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.51,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what club you're gonna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.47,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in radios?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.83,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that loser, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.89,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Two four-eyed bookworm runts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.63,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,They're made for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.83,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. Because of me, \Nthey picked on you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Infantile creeps like that can't do \Nanything unless they're in a pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.20,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested in radios, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.95,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun, one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:28.42,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a good idea to antagonize \Nthe guy who sits behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.83,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,He's a notorious thug that \Neven the teacher can't manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:36.70,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kawabuchi and if he \Nzeros in on you, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Just thinking about \Nit makes me feel nauseous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mukae Ritsuko, the class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:56.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was instructed to show you around \Nthe school during lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't feel sick anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So the gymnasium is back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And the infirmary is in this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay, Nishimi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha think you're doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.28,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! It slipped outta my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.36,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.19,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.86,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.13,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Never saw 'im before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:37.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Mukae-san, where's the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've moved from school to school \Never since first grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:49.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If something unexpected happened, \NI would lose my equilibrium,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and even minor stress would trigger nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:58.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But one time, I found a place at school \Nwhere I could regain my bearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If I can \Njust get to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why you holdin' my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that grabbed {\i1}my{\i0} hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I get it... You're the key burglar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I ain't gonna hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.33,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,You Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.18,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,This what you're lookin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then you goons are the thieves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:00.59,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,The roof belongs to us senior smokers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want the key to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:09.53,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,A candyass like you better \Nget the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You want the key that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a holda this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:13.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How reckless can you be, going \Nup against three seniors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,For 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you thought \NI'd give it to you gratis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I put my ass on the line gettin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.14,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I didn't even \Ngo to class once today, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.99,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,City boy like that's got no common \Nground with us country boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:56.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you, Sentaro! \NYou got in another fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some scratches...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.78,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:11.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna answer a guy \Nwho does nothin' but fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo! You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.89,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's Nishimi Kaoru-kun, a kid \Nthat just transferred in today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:22.56,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,supposed to be rich and a real brainiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, rich boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, your name is "Richie".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's me and you be pals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.34,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro's got a new target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.75,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,It's curtains for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.40,Main Dialog,Student,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I feel sick again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I've got a favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:54.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pay 100,000, but could you \Nlend me the key just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But right now it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's raining outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem if I take an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like fun! I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? This ain't much fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. I'm not up here to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then why bother comin' up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're bored, you can always go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Class ain't my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you take a shower, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scared of, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' good's ever come of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let yourself get a little wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,To the both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:47.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cause me no end of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We're going right to the infirmary \Nso you can borrow a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:56.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'll get your gym clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What, you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:27.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sort of... I play piano, \Nclassical music though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Classical, huh? What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:43.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice with the glasses on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but you have a really \Npretty face, Nishimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:51.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it rude to call a man \N"pretty"? I meant "handsome".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human hair dryer, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:07.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes again, bein' \Nscared. What a fraidy cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:10.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be afraid anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:19.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,After all... that rain felt great, \Nway better than I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:31.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even with everyone staring at \Nme, I can breathe normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:48.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to play the \Npiano, even being a sailor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:54.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, I'm going to be away \Nagain for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.07,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good boy while I'm gone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:00.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When I play the piano, I can \Nforget all of the bad stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and the loneliness from Dad being away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:10.68,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Kaoru. Your uncle \Nin Kyushu has a huge grand piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... I don't want a grand piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What I want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.91,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru-kun. You're up \Nreally early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.41,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play the piano? Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:40.29,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko feels like hearing \Na tune that'll wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But playing this early in \Nthe morning would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.80,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna hear it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.32,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko will take responsibility, so please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.88,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Please-please-please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.20,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.75,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the piano at this hour... \NDon't you have any sense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Aunt. Mariko-chan wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:30.32,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,See? This is why I told you to stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.33,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the blame on someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.80,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's difficult for a \Nfather to raise a child {\i1}alone{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:43.71,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's your mother who's responsible, \Nfor abandoning the both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro didn't come today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're lonely without him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I wasn't able to \Ncomprehend that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be quite pleased if he \Nsees fit to extend his absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:07.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... It looked to me like \Nyou two were hitting it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:14.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is afraid of Sentaro, \Nbut you act normally in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:19.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you and Sentaro could \Nbecome buddies, Nishimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-san... Give me a \Nbreak with that smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Really, as his childhood \Nfriend, I can guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:34.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Childhood friend...? So that's why you're \Nso casual with each other's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:38.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can call me by \Nmy name too, Nishimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:43.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe I'll call you... "Kaoru-san".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.91,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, Kaoru-san, Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:48.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this echoing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:51.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I said that without \Nasking. If you don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine! I don't mind it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right... Ri... chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know of a record shop \Nin town that sells classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Records? We've got tons \Nof records at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:13.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I really mean by inviting \Nyou over, don't you... Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:17.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think things are moving too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how Kyushu girls behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is our shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:27.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Fath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name is Nishimi Kaoru. Your \Ndaughter has been very kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The classical records are over \Non that shelf, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.88,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of records are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like piano music...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I play the piano myself, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You play the piano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:17:00.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko! Outsiders aren't allowed in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Kaoru-san is a good \Nfriend of mine and Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.04,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not his friend, just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doin' here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's what I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko! We got an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this, Sentaro! Kaoru-san \Nsays he can play piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But bet you anything it's just rich \Nkid stuffed shirt classical stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jazz is the only music for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san... Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kaoru-san, go on and play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:46.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, only jazz is allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:51.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the piano you want, I'll play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:03.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know this piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear any more. It's like {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! That ain't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! \NI played it exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.78,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you play it without feelin' it, \Nit don't sound like no jazz to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:29.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I'd love to hear you \Ntwo do a session together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru & Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, Ri'ko. That's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy don't get jazz and \Nhe's got no sense for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:41.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A little practice and \Nplaying that'll be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:42.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru & Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kaoru-san! Come back again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:58.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, do you know the name of the \Ntune he was playing on the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.34,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing Sen can play on \Nthe piano is the intro to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:09.55,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Art Blakey and the Jazz \NMessengers' "Moanin'".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he here to buy classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.83,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:37.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but his drums just wouldn't \Nstop thundering in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you walking strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is how I always walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko! Richie! See ya's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're running down this slope that \NI hate so much like it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What can you see beyond the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an outlook that I've never seen?
